Cells BHK-21 cells (American Type Culture Collection, USA) were cultured in modified essential eagle medium (Sigma, UK) supplemented with 10% foetal bovine serum, 2 mM L-glutamine, 100 U penicillin and 0.1 mg/ml streptomycin (Sigma). Chick Embryonic Fibroblast (CEF) cells (Institute for Animal Health, UK) were cultured in Dulbecco's modified eagle medium (Sigma) supplemented as above. SW13 and VeroE6 cells (European Collection of Cell Cultures, UK) were maintained in Leibovitz's L-15 medium containing Glutamax (Life Technologies, UK) supplemented with 10% foetal bovine serum (Sigma). 


